# Smart Spaced-Repetition Vocab Builder - Backend

Backend service for the Smart Spaced-Repetition Vocabulary Builder application.

Built using:

- Node.js
- Express.js
- MongoDB
- Mongoose

---

# Features

- Add new vocabulary words
- Fetch definitions from Dictionary API
- Store words in MongoDB
- Review words using spaced repetition
- Schedule future reviews
- Developer Test Mode support

